<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

  <title>Event Inviter — QR invitations & fast guest check-in</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Create events, build your guest list, and invite people by email, shareable link, or printable card. Every invitation carries a unique QR code for instant check-in at the door." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ appUrl }}/" />

  <!-- Open Graph -->
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="Event Inviter" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Event Inviter — QR invitations & fast guest check-in" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Invite guests by email, link, or printable card. Every invite has a unique QR code you scan at the door." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="{{ appUrl }}/" />

  <!-- Twitter -->
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Event Inviter — QR invitations & fast guest check-in" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Invite guests by email, link, or printable card. Every invite has a unique QR code you scan at the door." />

  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
      "name": "Event Inviter",
      "applicationCategory": "BusinessApplication",
      "operatingSystem": "Web",
      "description": "Create events, manage guest lists, and send QR-code invitations by email, link, or printable card with fast door check-in.",
      "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "USD" }
    }
  </script>

  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; color: #14110f; line-height: 1.5; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .wrap { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    header { height: 72px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .brand { font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
    .nav a { margin-left: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: #555; }
    .nav a:hover { color: #111; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #111827; color: #fff; padding: 12px 22px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; }
    .btn:hover { background: #1f2937; }
    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: #111827; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; }
    .hero { padding: 90px 0 70px; text-align: center; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 52px; letter-spacing: -1.5px; line-height: 1.05; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 21px; color: #4b5563; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 32px; }
    .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; }
    .features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; padding: 40px 0 90px; }
    .feature { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px; }
    .feature .ico { font-size: 28px; }
    .feature h3 { margin: 14px 0 8px; font-size: 19px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
    .feature p { color: #6b7280; }
    .steps { background: #f9fafb; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 70px 0; }
    .steps h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 34px; letter-spacing: -0.8px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .steps-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .step .n { width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 50%; background: #111827; color: #fff; display: grid; place-items: center; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .step h4 { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .step p { color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px; }
    .final { text-align: center; padding: 90px 0; }
    .final h2 { font-size: 36px; letter-spacing: -0.8px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 32px 0; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; }
    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .features, .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 38px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <div class="brand">Event Inviter</div>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn" style="padding: 9px 18px">Get started</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
  </div>

  <main>
    <section class="hero wrap">
      <h1>Invite guests. Scan a QR. Done.</h1>
      <p>
        Create your event, build a guest list, and send invitations by email, shareable link, or
        printable card. Every invite carries a unique QR code for instant check-in at the door.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="/signup" class="btn">Create your event — free</a>
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost">Login</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="wrap">
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="ico">✉️</div>
          <h3>Invite your way</h3>
          <p>Email, a shareable link, or a printed card — each guest gets their own unique QR code.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="ico">📷</div>
          <h3>Scan to check in</h3>
          <p>Open the scanner at the door and check guests in with your phone camera in seconds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="ico">🎨</div>
          <h3>Design custom cards</h3>
          <p>Build beautiful invitation cards with a drag-and-drop editor — QR code included.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="steps">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <div class="steps-grid">
          <div class="step"><div class="n">1</div><h4>Create an event</h4><p>Add the date, place, and details.</p></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="n">2</div><h4>Add guests</h4><p>Name is enough — email and phone are optional.</p></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="n">3</div><h4>Send invites</h4><p>Email, link, or printable card with a QR code.</p></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="n">4</div><h4>Check them in</h4><p>Scan the QR at the door. Instant verification.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="final wrap">
      <h2>Ready to host your next event?</h2>
      <a href="/signup" class="btn">Get started free</a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="wrap">© Event Inviter — QR invitations & guest check-in</div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
